      <li>Related software</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h3>Motivation</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>
        Theoretical lifetime predictions longer than measured values:
        \( \text{ms} \) vs. \( \text{ps} \)
      </li>
      <li>Finite contact resistance mismatch: a potential candidate</li>
      <li>Unified analytic solution for fitting data in all limits</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
