<section>
  <h2>Regimes</h2>
  <div>
    <h3>Zero field</h3>
    <p>$$\Delta R_{\text{NL}} = \left( P_{\Sigma}^L \right)^2 R_N e^{- L / \lambda}$$</p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h3>Tunneling contacts</h3>
    <p>$$f^{\infty} = \text{Re} {\frac{e^{- \left( L / \lambda \right) \sqrt{1 + i \omega \tau}}}{2 \sqrt{1 + i \omega \tau}}}$$</p>
  </div>

  <h3>Fits independent of lifetime</h3>
  <p>\( \lambda / r \gg \sqrt{\omega \tau} \gg 1 \)</p>
  <p>Zeros determined by
     $$L \sqrt{\frac{D}{2 \omega}} + \frac{\pi}{4} = \frac{n \pi}{2}$$</p>

  <p>{{cite references id="PhysRevB.89.245436"}}</p>
</section>

